Notable changes in flashtool:
=============================
Version 1.2:
- support reading data from a REU instead of disk
- add a minimal drive menu to send commands and
  change the current device number
- accept longer file names (up to 254 chars)
- actually use the offset in the hexdump menu option
- use a timeout to detect if no tapecart is connected
- minor changes to increase visual consistency of menus
